    dc:description "Fig. 1. Cynolebias parnaibensis, Jacobina do Piauí, Piauí, Brazil. (a) UFPB 6719, holotype, male, 54.5 mm SL. (b) UFPB 6709, paratype, female, 46.2 mm SL." ;
